# Bundle: Whisper STT model (~57 MB) is committed so the installer ships
# voice-ready. Silero VAD ONNX is feature-gated and not bundled by default;
# the negation is kept for the day someone enables silero-vad in releases.
!resources/models/whisper/*.bin
!resources/models/silero/*.onnx
